            <P>The GVS Transmedia Accelerator Program is less about incubating ideas and concepts in early stages but more about accelerating projects that have an existing foundation (i.e.: an existing script).</p>
            <h4>How much funding do selected companies receive?</h4>
            <p>Selected companies will receive $50K in seed investment funding from the GTA Development Fund. In addition, companies will receive dedicated mentoring and coaching over a 6-month intensive program to develop the franchise and position the company for raising follow on funding.</p>
            <h4>How much equity does the Fund take?</h4>
            <p>Selected companies will sell 10% equity of their company to the GTA Development Fund in exchange for the investment and to be coached through the GVS Transmedia Project Pipeline.</p>
            <h4>What is the GVS Transmedia Project Pipeline?</h4>
            <p>The Transmedia Project Pipeline is about developing your franchise to the stage of potential to be funded and produced. The Pipeline is not about producing your franchise’s products but rather developing it to the stage where it has potential to be funded and produced.</p>
