            <h4>What does the application process involve?</h4>
            <p>The application is available on our website at <a href="http://www.globalvirtualstudio.com/accelerator ">www.globalvirtualstudio.com/accelerator</a></p>
            <p>The application process will require candidates to submit current drafts of their lead product’s script and show proof of chain of title.</p>

            <h4>How many companies will be accepted?</h4>
            <p>An average of six companies will be selected per cycle.</p>
            <h4>When is the Application period?</h4>
            <p>For its first cycle, the Program will be accepting applications from April 11, 2014 through May 9, 2014.</p>
            <h4>When does the first cycle’s intensive program start?</h4>
            <p>The first cycle will begin upon final selection of the cohort startup companies. We project early June 2014.</p>
